title: Ranpak Ready Roll natural Packing Paper 30 ft x 14 in | Honeycomp Wrapping Paper | sustainable, environmentally friendly, 100% paper made in the USA
description: The Ready Roll honeycomb packaging paper gives your products strong and shock absorbing protection. Wrapped products are protected damage during shipment. The paper protects your valuables thanks to its innovative structure of die cut and tissue paper. The combination protects from dents, scratches or damage caused by surface abrasion. The recyclable material requires 20% less material compared to conventional packaging solutions. It ensures a higher protection and ensures a lower return rate. The wrapping paper roll is easy to use. The kraft paper can be torn off by hand at any point so no scissors are needed. The paper interlocks to itself thanks to the innovative honeycomb structure, eliminating the need for packaging tape. The wrap is made from 100% paper, making it a sustainable alternative conventional packaging material. Break new ground with this recycled paper when shipping your products and ensure sustainable packaging management. With our wrapping paper, gifts can be wrapped in a natural look. It is ideal for shipping and moving or for packing plates, cups, glasses, dishes or other delicate objects.
